In re THE WILCOX & WHITE CO. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. December 22, 1922.) No. 115. Leo Oppenheimer, of New York City (Samuel H. Kaufman and Milton P. Kupfer, both of New York City, of counsel), for trustee. Slade, Slade & Slade, of New York City, for Horton Printing Co.

Before ROGERS, HOUGH and MAYER, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Orders affirmed.
